{"tid":1468429,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"政府嚴厲譴責示威者在機場暴力行為","createTime":"2019-08-13T18:38:59.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-13T18:41:29.000Z","uid":2126,"like":0,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"442dd0629efc3d73d0bee5a41a6123407b61e397","tid":1468429,"uid":2126,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T18:38:59.000Z","msg":"政府發言人就昨晚示威者在機場的暴力行為，予以最嚴厲的譴責，稱警方一定會嚴正追究，將涉案者繩之於法。<br />\n<br />\n發言人說，昨天自下午起大批示威者在機場集結，癱瘓機場運作，嚴重影響出入境旅客，已遠超和平示威行為，並形容有暴徒行為變本加厲，分別包圍及毆打一名旅客及一名記者，並阻止救護人員將該名旅客送院。<br />\n<br />\n警方到場處理事件時，多名暴徒更襲擊警務人員，嚴重威脅警務人員人身安全。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1474493-20190814.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1474493-20190814.htm&d=cw67THcQ8%2BNa%2BfcBlgGHU8QVtcXcndjic5JqfcA1BWo%3D&h=39477825\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1474493-20190814.htm&h=ce9bede9\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1474493-20190814.htm</a>"},{"pid":"1eba76d6a57038e387cf7a3ccc4f4f8b74496773","tid":1468429,"uid":260088,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T18:39:28.000Z","msg":"<strong><ins>唔割席</ins></strong><br />\n<br />\n［置頂］［緊急］ 民間記者會請幫手<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1466254\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1466254</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\">民間記者會要AM開</span><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">如果大量的道歉，跟政府形成對比，可能仲有得救</span></span><br />\n3日不入機場<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.scmp.com/news/hong-kong/politics/article/3022668/riot-police-protesters-clash-unprecedented-violence-hong\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.scmp.com%2Fnews%2Fhong-kong%2Fpolitics%2Farticle%2F3022668%2Friot-police-protesters-clash-unprecedented-violence-hong&d=cw67THcQ8%2BNa%2BfcBlgGHU8QVtcXcndjic5JqfcA1B